Package: muxkit
Architecture: any
Depends: ${shlibs:Depends}, ${misc:Depends}
Description: Lightweight terminal multiplexer written in C
 muxkit enables multiple terminal sessions to be created, accessed,
 and controlled from a single screen. Sessions can be detached and
 continue running in the background, then later reattached.
 .
 Features include session management, multiple panes, scrollback
 history, internationalization, and daemon mode.
